description:
Fuel up for Finals!
Trojans, join us in our Culinary Classroom to learn easy meals that you can make at home.&nbsp; Get ready for a hands on cooking experience with USC Hospitality Chefs and our registered dietitian that will boost your confidence and learn valuable lessons on health and nutrition.&nbsp; Spots are on a first come first serve basis.
With finals around the corner, our focus this evening will take a deep dive into how nutrition impacts your performance in the classroom.&nbsp; &nbsp; Our featured dish will include good mood foods with the macro and micronutrients you need to perform like the academic athlete that you are!&nbsp;

Feeling stressed about finals? Take a moment to relax and reset with Mindful USC and RA Veronica! There will be a workshop on mindfulness, a meditation session, and FREE SMOOTHIES FROM SUNLIFE ORGANICS!
&nbsp;
(Event specific to Birnkrant residents)

Come out for free Kona Shaved Ice!!!
